<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"Header"</Bold> sets the Header of the ChartArea. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Font Family"</Bold> sets the Font Family of the ChartArea. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"Font Size"</Bold> sets the size of the font in ChartArea. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The combo box <Bold>"Foreground"</Bold> sets the foregroud color of the font in ChartArea. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

<ListItem>
<Paragraph>The text box <Bold>"Height"</Bold> sets the height of the ChartArea. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>

</List>


